text.section:
The plan shall include:
The number of institution residents on waiting lists for placement in the community;
The number of persons outside institutions on waiting lists for placement in the institution;
The number of persons for whom no placement is made nor services provided because of a lack of community resources;
The number, type, nature, and cost of services necessary for placement to occur;
The status of compliance with the plan;
The cabinets' specific efforts to increase residential and institutional services and documentation of the success of these efforts; and
The specific plans for new efforts to enhance the opportunities for persons with developmental disabilities to move into less restrictive environments.
